"PlusOne" is a beautiful but also useful counter. You can create your own counting items with you favorite style, and track their changes persistently.

=== FEATURES ===

◆ Create counting items, with so many style combination;
◆ Review changes over time by line chart;
◆ Review and amend changes you make at some day in a calendar;
◆ Use Siri shortcut to update counting items;
◆ Use widget to update counting items;
◆ Share your achievement to friends with elegant image;

=== USAGE ===

◆ Habit formation;
◆ Daily punch;
◆ Event counting;

